WEBVTT

00:00:01.839 --> 00:00:12.479
You saw the straightforward spot on doing it. I think so. Okay.

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:35.255
Are we live? Yep. Well, good morning. Are they here yet? Yeah, there it is.

00:00:35.256 --> 00:00:42.739
Yep. They say we're here. We've got nine. Well, thank you all for joining us today.

00:00:42.740 --> 00:00:46.755
Good morning, family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining us.

00:00:46.756 --> 00:00:52.799
You know, I have some things on my heart to pray about tonight. It's important.

00:00:52.800 --> 00:01:00.078
You know, we see all the things in the news already about the attacks that we saw in Minnesota today.

00:01:00.079 --> 00:01:05.353
The man tried to hurt the people in the church, but the Lord protected every single one of them.

00:01:05.354 --> 00:01:11.286
And that's exactly what we're expecting: for God to show up and intervene like that.

00:01:11.287 --> 00:01:16.478
When that man—I don't know, I guess they hit him with a truck and all that, and then the security guy.

00:01:16.479 --> 00:01:23.168
That's why the Lord—remember, I had you all, I said you must pray about security over your churches in the days ahead.

00:01:23.169 --> 00:01:29.517
And there's a lot of people that come against that, but I'm telling you what the spirit of the Lord said: pray for security in your churches.

00:01:29.518 --> 00:01:32.955
And some people can't afford that, but there are some people that can.

00:01:32.956 --> 00:01:37.564
And so that is what the Lord was showing me, and there will be more of this.

00:01:37.565 --> 00:01:41.538
And that was with the man that I saw. Most people say, "Well, he lives in America now.

00:01:41.539 --> 00:01:52.095
This powerful, you know, he has a lot of finances."This guy coming against, trying to bring chaos in the spirit realm about mass shootings in churches.

00:01:52.096 --> 00:01:58.655
And then I saw the one in Denver, and I warned you all in the days ahead there.

00:01:58.656 --> 00:02:08.154
I saw a man dressed up in military garb, and he had a bulletproof-looking vest on, and he had a ballistic-looking helmet.

00:02:08.155 --> 00:02:13.304
He had a helmet on, and he walked into the crowd, and he started mowing people down with an AR-15.

00:02:13.305 --> 00:02:25.056
And the Lord said, "These things like this, you take your authority and stop these attacks that are planned by the enemy."And it was that place, and I saw some other place.

00:02:25.058 --> 00:02:36.472
I'm trying to remember. I see so much, you all, that I have my son and my wife—they have to take notes and help me because I said, "Lord,"because He downloads to me all the time. It was like today.

00:02:36.473 --> 00:02:48.318
I mean, it's like an open heaven, and I just sit there and just listen, talking to the Father, and He's talking, saying, "Brandon, it's time for My body—for Me to talk to you shouldn't be abnormal.

00:02:48.319 --> 00:03:01.518
I want to talk to My body all the time. If you're plugged into the electrical socket, you're going to get power, right?"So, we're plugged into the Word, we're plugged into Him, and we're hearing Him on a day-to-day basis.

00:03:01.519 --> 00:03:11.482
Are people coming, praying over churches? Yeah. So, we have some people. I just want to make sure people are seeing it.

00:03:11.483 --> 00:03:16.696
I know people are watching the Thunder game, so I didn't want to interrupt it, but I just feel an urgency to pray.

00:03:16.697 --> 00:03:31.863
And so, I thought, "Well, I'm sorry to disrupt your Thunder game, but we have some business to take care of in the spirit realm concerning the days ahead."And it's very serious that the body of Christ does this together.

00:03:31.864 --> 00:03:42.079
I usually just do a video right now, but I feel we're changing things when we're praying as a group, and we're just plowing over the enemy.

00:03:42.080 --> 00:03:58.274
So, what I feel an urgency about right now is still the churches in the days ahead, praying over megachurches, places of worship for mass shootings and things like that. Praying for protection over our leaders.

00:03:58.275 --> 00:04:14.875
And I told you all I saw—you know, and I've tried not to always rehearse this—but I saw a mega-preacher in Texas, and I told you to pray for that man, and I said to pray over the preacher in Tampa, and to pray over the person in North Carolina.

00:04:14.876 --> 00:04:21.739
The Lord gives me certain megachurches that were targets, and the Lord said, "Pray over this,"but it's more than that.

00:04:21.740 --> 00:04:29.050
So we look, and right now we have the one in Minnesota, and I didn't even know what that church—I don't even know what denomination it was, but it doesn't matter, folks.

00:04:29.051 --> 00:04:31.695
Do you understand the enemy's coming after everybody he can?

00:04:31.696 --> 00:04:37.858
And so that's why we raise up our voices and pray in the Holy Ghost and put a bloodline around our buildings.

00:04:37.859 --> 00:04:51.568
You need to plead the blood over your church, going around taking your authority and taking it over your children when they go back to school in the fall, praying a hedge of protection over what belongs to us.

00:04:51.569 --> 00:04:57.887
That no weapon formed against you is going to prosper. And it is important that you do this not just one time.

00:04:57.888 --> 00:05:01.286
"Well, we did it one time. Well, you know, we talked about it.

00:05:01.287 --> 00:05:07.853
What did we—we did that about a month ago."No, this is something that you do repetitively all the time.

00:05:07.854 --> 00:05:12.517
Every day you wake up and you take that seat of authority according to Ephesians.

00:05:12.518 --> 00:05:21.196
You need to read Ephesians, go over Ephesians talking about how we're seated with Him in the heavenlies, and you take that place of authority every single day.

00:05:21.197 --> 00:05:28.602
I do not let one day go by without pleading the blood, taking communion, seeking Him daily.

00:05:28.603 --> 00:05:42.963
This has become—I don't want to say it's a routine, but it is like brushing your teeth, combing your hair (whatever, if you have hair, not like me)—doing this every day.

00:05:42.964 --> 00:05:54.046
And when your kids get ready to go back to school, if they're in public school, go around pleading the blood over things, saying, "Father, as my child is in that building, I put a bloodline. We put angels around this building.

00:05:54.047 --> 00:06:07.999
Father, I thank You, Lord, that You said that You send Your angels to keep charge over us, and they will bear us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against the stone."I believe, Father, that those angels are protecting my babies.

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:16.502
You must use your authority in the days ahead. "Well, we're going to go to the high school football game, we're going to go to the college game, we're going to—"no, no.

00:06:16.503 --> 00:06:25.493
I plead the blood. I thank You, Lord, that the blood of Jesus is covering my children, covering us as we go to these sporting events or whatever you plan on doing.

00:06:25.494 --> 00:06:30.354
"We're going to go to a Major League game or whatever."We thank You, Lord.

00:06:30.355 --> 00:06:35.839
The angels go with me everywhere I go. You know, I see these posts on Facebook.

00:06:35.840 --> 00:06:41.870
They'll say, "The angel..."—you know, the man's there, and these demons are there trying to mess with them, and the angels come in and start beating up on the demon.

00:06:41.871 --> 00:06:47.911
And I said, "Well, I have to disagree with that post a little bit because my angels never leave.

00:06:47.912 --> 00:06:52.276
They're always there, and they're always ready to defend me.

00:06:52.277 --> 00:07:14.191
I'm not having to call them down to help me out because they're already there."Yes, with their swords and their shields ready, and they're up there going, "Man, I'm ready to bust some devil in the head."They come around here and they're going, "Well, my angels are far off in the distant future."Because that post was like, "Hey, that guy was praying, these devils are there."I don't know if anybody saw that, but they're all there, and these devils are there, and they're growling in the background.

00:07:14.192 --> 00:07:19.796
You could see them, and the guy's in the bed, and he's praying, and all of a sudden the angels show up, and I was like, "No, no, no, no.

00:07:19.797 --> 00:07:24.574
My angels never leave. My angels are always on guard."I've got some big ones.

00:07:24.575 --> 00:07:30.159
I always say his name is Big George. I've always named him because he's never told me his name.

00:07:30.160 --> 00:07:36.043
And so people go, "Why do you call him Big George?"Because I said, "I don't know, it just felt like such an old country name."So I named my angel Big George.

00:07:36.044 --> 00:07:40.879
And people don't like that, but that's my angel. I call him what I want to.

00:07:40.880 --> 00:07:47.927
And so Big George is always here, ready to protect me. I've seen him multiple times, and he's a big old guy.

00:07:47.928 --> 00:07:57.672
He's a big old sausage-fingers and big hands. And it's amazing, you know, the things the Lord will allow me to see.

00:07:57.673 --> 00:08:01.846
I've told you all, He'll even allow me to see when they're protecting me.

00:08:01.847 --> 00:08:18.022
When I'm pumping gas and I'm in a sketchy neighborhood, the angels are there, and I see him there, and I'm—you know, you don't want to be fearful, but you're always on alert, looking around like, "Oh man, I'm in a bad neighborhood."And then there's Big George sitting there, standing there, and he's watching out.

00:08:18.023 --> 00:08:23.342
He's always at attention, watching over me. And I say, "Thank you, Father, for your angels.

00:08:23.343 --> 00:08:29.437
We need to utilize them more and more in the days ahead."Angels unaware.

00:08:29.438 --> 00:08:38.338
I believe that God gives his angels to protect us, and I always say, "Father, I commission my angels. Father, I thank you that the angels are protecting us.

00:08:38.339 --> 00:08:45.191
Thank you, Lord, that no weapon formed against me is going to prosper."And people, we forget about it.

00:08:45.192 --> 00:08:48.680
It's the unseen realm. You know, people don't always use that.

00:08:48.681 --> 00:08:56.616
"Oh well, you know, the unseen realm, whatever."No, no, no. I believe that every one of us has angels that watch over us.

00:08:56.617 --> 00:08:59.439
Believers, believing believers, I believe they're watching.

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:02.667
Angels are watching over your children; they're watching over you.

00:09:02.668 --> 00:09:19.119
And it's time we become more strong about doing that, not sitting back going, "Well, you know, every once in a while."No, I do it every day, every day, all the time. Even when I'm driving: "Angels, protect us as we drive.

00:09:19.120 --> 00:09:40.559
Father, I cover us with the mighty name of Jesus over our house, over our car as we drive down the highway, over our tires, over everything, that, Father, we make it there safe and we make it back safe, and that, Father, we are always covered by your blood and your angels are watching over us."And that's what you're going to have to do in the days ahead more and more.

00:09:40.560 --> 00:09:46.655
That's what Psalm 91 even talks about, that he gives his angels charge over us.

00:09:46.656 --> 00:09:56.159
So, I'm trying to give you some encouragement today that we're not going to be afraid of the terror by night, nor for the arrow that flieth by day.

00:09:56.160 --> 00:10:04.639
We're not going to be afraid of those things because Jesus Christ has sent his angels to protect us, and he has given his word that we could use it as a weapon.

00:10:04.640 --> 00:10:10.145
It's our sword. And so, that's what we're going to do. And yeah, I see these things and what the Lord shows me is coming.

00:10:10.146 --> 00:10:18.078
But I'm telling you folks, the believers, us, the people that are watching this broadcast, I believe we have a special covering.

00:10:18.079 --> 00:10:27.999
And I said I'm not participating in mass casualties. We're not going to participate in a financial disaster.

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:31.595
We're always going to be above and not beneath. We're going to go through and not go under.

00:10:31.596 --> 00:10:40.489
I don't know about you, ladies and gentlemen, but I know that God is able to protect me, and he's an ever-present help in a time of need, and he's going to watch over us.

00:10:40.490 --> 00:10:45.299
And so I try to encourage you. Yeah, these volcanoes I've seen erupting.

00:10:45.300 --> 00:10:51.834
I've seen earthquakes in diverse places. I've seen major storms, mega-major hurricanes in the days ahead.

00:10:51.835 --> 00:11:09.276
I saw a great hurricane coming, and I saw it being seeded, and I saw the eyewall was so tight and it was very, very strong, kind of like the one that hit Florida and went up through North Carolina and caused all that damage.

00:11:09.277 --> 00:11:20.086
I'm talking about a major hurricane coming, and the Lord said, "Poke the eyewall out."Don't pray for it to go to Fort Myers or to Tampa or to Destin or whatever.

00:11:20.087 --> 00:11:26.093
When we take authority over it, we poke the eyewall out. Make it fall apart, Lord.

00:11:26.094 --> 00:11:33.139
Because, you know, I always see believers when they're praying in that area: "Oh, go this way. Go that way. No, no, no, go down here.

00:11:33.140 --> 00:11:38.479
Don't go down here."But what we need to do is use our faith and say, "Father, you weaken that thing.

00:11:38.480 --> 00:11:46.572
It's a tropical storm now, or a depression, or whatever. We're not going to have a major hurricane this year."That's the kind of authority.

00:11:46.573 --> 00:11:51.608
"As he is, so are we in this world."That's what the Bible says.

00:11:51.609 --> 00:12:01.813
Now, people would argue with that all the time, but that's what the Bible says: "As he is, so are we in this world."And if Jesus could do it, he gave us the authority to do it also.

00:12:01.814 --> 00:12:10.391
Why? Because he dwells on the inside of me. And I believe we can pray over the storms and tell them, "Peace, be still,"just like Jesus did in that boat.

00:12:10.392 --> 00:12:17.082
He was resting, and the disciples were freaking out, but he wasn't. He was asleep. So there was a peace there.

00:12:17.083 --> 00:12:27.084
And when you have that inward peace, that peace that passes all understanding, that's why I say we've got to follow our peace in everything we do.

00:12:27.085 --> 00:12:31.689
If it costs you your peace, it's too expensive. Yes. But I say that's why you follow your peace.

00:12:31.690 --> 00:12:37.483
And people, you know, that's why I say I don't make a big decision until I have peace. We talk about it all the time.

00:12:37.484 --> 00:12:46.976
If it's financial, say if it's buying a car or maybe a house or a job offer or whatever, you follow your peace.

00:12:46.977 --> 00:12:53.747
And if you don't have peace, don't do it, because that Prince of Peace is dwelling on the inside of you.

00:12:53.748 --> 00:12:57.964
And if you have that inward check, and that's the Holy Spirit scratching you saying, "Don't do that.

00:12:57.965 --> 00:13:01.838
You're making a bad choice right now. You're about to make a really dumb choice.

00:13:01.839 --> 00:13:09.999
Don't do that,"and you go, "Well, you know, hon"— so I told her, I said, "You know, I just don't feel peace about going to that place.

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:14.419
I don't feel peace about going to that vacation spot or whatever.

00:13:14.420 --> 00:13:20.769
Let's follow the voice of the Lord."And that's why I say I always inquire of the Lord in everything I do.

00:13:20.770 --> 00:13:32.425
No matter where I go, I say, "Is it meant for me to go there today?"And I believe as the day approaches and it gets darker and darker like I've told you is coming, we always ask him every morning.

00:13:32.426 --> 00:13:44.633
Father, I thank you, Lord, because the people on 9/11, there were a lot of people that were supposed to be there and they didn't show up that day. But are they the ones that inquired of the Lord?

00:13:44.634 --> 00:13:59.332
"Father, I don't feel that peace today."We heard a story by Brother Hagin, and he was talking about one of his members, that the pastors were praying over some of the members and they said, "I feel something really bad.

00:13:59.333 --> 00:14:07.002
We need to pray."And they knew five members were out on vacation, so they kept interceding all night long.

00:14:07.003 --> 00:14:16.479
And I want to make this short for y'all because I know you have things you've got to do, but I feel I'm supposed to tell you this.

00:14:16.480 --> 00:14:30.845
They started praying and they interceded for hours, and they still couldn't get a release, and they thought, "Man, something's really wrong still."And so these two prayer warriors, the pastors of the church, kept praying for their members of the church.

00:14:30.846 --> 00:14:35.093
Well, they stopped after three or four times of getting up in the middle of the night, kept praying.

00:14:35.094 --> 00:14:41.919
He said, "Well, whoever this is, Lord, let them have a dream.

00:14:41.920 --> 00:14:57.565
Let them have a dream and tell them in their dream whatever the caution is, what we're feeling and we're interceding."So the next day, their children's church worker, one of the people there over the children's church, went to the job site.

00:14:57.566 --> 00:15:12.543
And he told the guy, because the guy that was normally there didn't come in to work that day, and he said, "Hey, why don't you go..."— there was an oil rig — and he told him, he said, "I want you to go up there and help out with this lift or whatever.

00:15:12.544 --> 00:15:27.544
You do it instead. You do it instead."And he said, "Last night, I had a dream, and in the dream I saw that wire right there break free, and it cut my head off and it fell to the ground.

00:15:27.545 --> 00:15:44.030
So, I don't feel peace about going up there."And so he told the guy, "I'm sorry, I can't do it."Well, the other guy, who was from the church across town that did not believe in the baptism of the Holy Ghost and didn't believe all this stuff, he said, "I'm not superstitious.

00:15:44.031 --> 00:16:03.359
I'll go up there and do the job."So he ran up the side of that thing, and five minutes into it, the wire snapped and cut that man's head off, and it bumped that guy who was praying in the spirit in his back.

00:16:03.360 --> 00:16:08.922
So it was a leading of the Lord trying to warn them that there was something wrong with it, but he went with his peace.

00:16:08.923 --> 00:16:15.599
Now the other guy didn't believe anything, and, you know, things happened with Christians, but one prayed in tongues.

00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:21.005
Yeah, one prayed in tongues, one prayed in the spirit. Sometimes we don't know what we're supposed to be praying, right?

00:16:21.006 --> 00:16:29.439
What is this that I feel? What is this caution? And so when praying in tongues, you have the gift of praying in tongues.

00:16:29.440 --> 00:16:34.074
And that's what we pray in the spirit all the time. Diana and I pray in the spirit all the time.

00:16:34.075 --> 00:16:42.586
And not saying that one's better than the other, but one's tapped into the spirit realm a little bit more than the other, you know, and that's what I'm trying to tell y'all.

00:16:42.587 --> 00:16:50.251
Being baptized in the Holy Ghost, but I felt an urgency following that peace because the other man followed the peace, and the other man didn't know peace.

00:16:50.252 --> 00:16:54.523
He's not here anymore, of course. And the other guy, he was a teaching superintendent.

00:16:54.524 --> 00:17:00.221
He was over the children's ministry, and his life was spared.

00:17:00.222 --> 00:17:04.702
But if the boss would have listened to him and said, 'You know what?

00:17:04.703 --> 00:17:13.838
We should probably check that wire then,'you know, we probably should check that wire, he would have found out that there was something wrong with it.

00:17:13.839 --> 00:17:22.558
But just follow it. What I'm trying to tell you is don't—the reason I brought all that up is don't ignore the peace.

00:17:22.559 --> 00:17:28.944
Follow it in the days ahead, and it will keep you and protect you. You must follow the peace of God.

00:17:28.945 --> 00:17:52.514
And when we go through all these things that are coming, I pray, 'Father, I'm always in the right place at the right time doing exactly what you've asked me to do for that day, and I will not miss it because you said that your children will hear your voice, a strange voice they will not follow.'And that's what I expect from it.

00:17:52.515 --> 00:17:57.669
I expect to hear you, Father. I expect when people say, 'Well, I don't hear God like you, Brandon.

00:17:57.670 --> 00:18:06.558
I don't hear God like you, Diana.'Yes, you do. You know what? It didn't come overnight. It comes by practice.

00:18:06.559 --> 00:18:14.902
It comes by—'faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the word of God.'But hearing his voice, too, comes by deliberately trying.

00:18:14.903 --> 00:18:25.554
And I say, 'Lord, I'm practicing your presence today.'I'm not saying I have it right all the time, but you know, as you grow, you get better at something.

00:18:25.555 --> 00:18:31.362
It's like riding a bike, walking, or whatever. Like a child, you keep falling, but you keep getting yourself back up.

00:18:31.363 --> 00:18:39.839
And people say, 'Well, you know, I'm embarrassed to say that or that.'No, no, no, folks. I've missed it a lot in the past. But you know what happens?

00:18:39.840 --> 00:18:45.358
The more you practice, the more you stand, the more you read his word, you're going to get better and better at it.

00:18:45.359 --> 00:18:50.443
And I say, 'Lord, I thank you. Man, that was embarrassing.'Well, that's all right.

00:18:50.444 --> 00:18:54.239
I pick myself up, brush yourself off, and just keep walking it out.

00:18:54.240 --> 00:19:04.402
Nobody's perfect, and nobody's going to get it right 99.9% of the time, 100% of the time, whatever. I'm just saying that's how you practice.

00:19:04.403 --> 00:19:15.451
You practice the voice and hearing the voice of God by his word, getting in the word, listening to him, and you say, 'Lord,'you may say, 'Well, I'm just going to keep doing it.'That's how you get good at it.

00:19:15.452 --> 00:19:20.719
How does a professional basketball player become the best and become MVP?

00:19:20.720 --> 00:19:25.393
Practice, practice. It's the same with football and everything else.

00:19:25.394 --> 00:19:28.954
I'm just comparing it to sports because that's what you maybe can relate with.

00:19:28.955 --> 00:19:37.457
A race car driver gets to be the best because he practices. And as you practice, you become, like I said, a champion.

00:19:37.458 --> 00:19:42.719
The only way you're going to become a champion is if you become good at the fundamentals.

00:19:42.720 --> 00:19:47.469
You have to become good at the fundamentals first so that you hear the voice of God.

00:19:47.470 --> 00:19:53.839
And the fundamentals of Christianity are going to church, reading your Bible, and praying.

00:19:53.840 --> 00:20:00.173
And those are the fundamentals, but you go back to the ABCs. Everybody wants to go to algebra and skip the ABCs.

00:20:00.174 --> 00:20:07.995
But everything in Christianity is based off of the ABCs first, and that's how you keep going from glory to glory to glory.

00:20:07.996 --> 00:20:15.678
But if you forget your fundamentals and the ABCs, you're not going to remember how to do the algebra equation.

00:20:15.679 --> 00:20:25.359
And you're going to be looking at it going, 'Man, I don't know.'And that's why I say if I get off track and you're going, 'Man, I feel I'm a little lost here,'go back to the basics.

00:20:25.360 --> 00:20:29.750
What got you there in the first place? 'Well, I'm a little off today.

00:20:29.751 --> 00:20:39.839
What's going on?'No, it's not panic time. It's go-back-to-the-basics time. Because back to the basics, the ABCs, is the foundation.

00:20:39.840 --> 00:20:54.558
And if you—the foundation is the word, and you get this beautiful book down inside of you and you don't turn away from it, and you get down and pray, that's when you're not a goose in the fog anymore, and you're all of a sudden going, 'Hey, I found my heading.

00:20:54.559 --> 00:21:00.825
I know where I'm going now because I went back to the basics.'But people try to make things in Christianity too complicated.

00:21:00.826 --> 00:21:10.558
But he made it so that a child can do it. Your five-year-old little child can have a relationship with the Lord and hear him every day.

00:21:10.559 --> 00:21:22.676
He didn't make it where, 'Well, you know, you're not a super adult Christian, so only the people who are college Christians can hear the voice of the Lord.'No, he made it so that a child can listen to him.

00:21:22.677 --> 00:21:27.172
A child can live by faith. God didn't make it hard. We make it hard.

00:21:27.173 --> 00:21:30.716
'Well, you know, God doesn't talk to me.'No, he does talk to you.

00:21:30.717 --> 00:21:37.833
I say my Father is always there, and he's willing to talk to me because why? He loves me.

00:21:37.834 --> 00:21:50.006
If we really, truly realized how much God loves us, if we really, truly realized how much he cares for us—and people go, 'Well, does God love me?'Yes, yes.

